name: Toy World
detail_description: The Super Robot action figure is equipped with lights, sounds, and movable joints. It comes with various accessories and is perfect for imaginative play.

name: Playtime Emporium
detail_description: The Princess Castle playset includes a beautifully designed castle, princess dolls, furniture, and accessories. It provides hours of imaginative play for kids.

name: RC Fun
detail_description: This high-speed remote control car can perform stunts, has responsive controls, and a durable design. It's a perfect gift for kids who love racing and adventures.

name: Brain Teasers Inc.
detail_description: The Puzzle Cube challenges your problem-solving skills. It's a classic toy that stimulates the mind and offers hours of fun. Suitable for all ages.

name: Creative Kids
detail_description: The Art Set contains a variety of art supplies including colored pencils, paints, brushes, and sketching pads. It's perfect for young artists and encourages creativity.

name: Prehistoric World
detail_description: The Dinosaur Playset includes various dinosaur figures, trees, and rocks. It provides a realistic prehistoric environment for kids to enjoy imaginative play.

name: Block Masters
detail_description: The Building Blocks set features colorful interlocking blocks that allow kids to create endless structures. It enhances motor skills and fosters creativity.

name: Tiny Tots
detail_description: The Tea Party Set includes a teapot, cups, saucers, and play food. It allows children to host their own tea parties and encourages social interaction.

name: Melody Makers
detail_description: The Musical Keyboard features multiple instrument sounds, rhythms, and demo songs. It introduces kids to the world of music and helps develop musical skills.

name: Active Kids
detail_description: The Sports Ball Set includes a soccer ball, basketball, and football. It promotes active play, coordination, and outdoor fun for kids of all ages.

name: Science Explorers
detail_description: The Science Kit contains various experiments and materials to explore the wonders of science. It encourages curiosity and learning in a fun way.

name: Mystic Wonders
detail_description: The Magic Set includes a variety of tricks, props, and a guidebook to perform amazing magic tricks. It sparks imagination and provides endless entertainment.
